@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Line Notify";
}

    <div class="row">
        <div>
            <h2>1.  註冊與登入</h2>
            <h3>申請Line帳號</h3>
            <h5>必須先有Line帳號，才能啟用LineNotify功能。</h5>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>2.  登錄LineNotify服務</h2>
            <h3>2-1.  連結申請 <a href="https://notify-bot.line.me/zh_TW/" target="_blank">連接</a></h3>
            <h3>2-2.  點選下方登錄服務</h3>
            <h3>2-3.	登入Line帳號</h3>
            <h5>
                設定的服務名稱、服務概要、服務網址 等等必填欄位，其中<samp class="point">Callback URL</samp>設定為http://localhost:64005/Home/GetCallback(<samp class="point">此為本專案API服務使用，若有異動則需變更URL位置</samp>)，會於LineNotify認證oAuth2機制時的畫面顯示。
            </h5>
            <h5>
                補充說明：<p>1. Callback URL請填入接收Code的網頁網址，在LineNotify連動成功時，會將authorize code傳至設定的返回網址，而返回網址需在Callback URL設定中存在，最多可設定5組Callback URL。</p>
                <p>2.電子郵件帳號欄位為第一次使用服務時的認證需要回信箱點取驗證</p>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <h3>請至管理登入服務下取得下方欄位</h3>
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                    <span class="input-group-text">Client ID:</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="txtClientID" placeholder="請填入Client ID">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                    <span class="input-group-text">Client Secret:</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="txtClientSecret" placeholder="請填入Client Secret">
            </div>
            <button onclick="Auth();" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info">點選這裡連結到Line Notify設定與並連動並帶回Token </button>

    </div>


<style>
    .point {
        color: red
    }
</style>



<script>
    function Auth() {
        var clientID = document.getElementById('txtClientID');
        var clientSecret = document.getElementById('txtClientSecret');
        if (clientID.value != "") {
            document.cookie = 'clientSecret=' + clientSecret.value;
            document.cookie = 'clientID=' + clientID.value;
            //if (clientSecret.value == "") {
            //    alert("清輸入Client ID");
            //    return;
            //} else {
            //    //檢查Cookie
            //    var clientSecret = getCookie("clientSecret");
            //    if (clientSecret != "") {
            //        //設定Cookie
            //          setCookie("clientSecret", clientSecret.value)
            //    }
            //    else {
            //         clearCookie(name);
            //         setCookie("clientSecret", clientSecret.value)
            //    }
            //}
          
            var URL = 'https://notify-bot.line.me/oauth/authorize?';
            URL += 'response_type=code';
            URL += '&client_id=' + clientID.value;
            URL += '&redirect_uri=http://localhost:64005/Home/GetCallback';
            URL += '&scope=notify';
            URL += '&state=abcde';
            window.location.href = URL;
            //window.open(URL, 'Auth', config = 'height=500,width=500');
        }
        else {
            alert("清輸入Client ID");
            return;
        }
    }
   






</script>